<L>__{exterior miami airport, curbside day}
<A>__{welles comes outside, squinting in the sun, moving down the sidewalk, looking back over his shoulder... the young republican is lead to a waiting limo by a driver. welles moves to the nearby taxi stand...}
<L>__{interior taxi day}
<A>__{welles gets in, turning in his seat to watch behind.}
<C>__{cab driver}
<D>__{where to?}
<A>__{welles keeps watching, sees the limo pull away and pass.}
<C>__{welles}
<D>__{follow that limousine. don't get too close, don't let it get too far away. just keep with it.}
<C>__{cab driver}
<D>__{you kidding?}
<C>__{welles}
<D>__{nope.}
<A>__{the cab set in motion. welles takes out cigarettes, lighting one, takes out a small notepad and makes notations.}
<C>__{cab driver}
<D>__{uh, listen... you're not supposed to be smoking in here. i'm sorry, that's company policy...}
